text: Sergey Stepanovich Ling (; ; born 7 May 1937) is a Belarusian politician and agronomist. He was Prime Minister of Belarus from 1996 to 2000 and Permanent Representative of Belarus to the United Nations from 2000 to 2002. ==References== Category:1937 births Category:Living people Category:Prime ministers of Belarus Category:Ambassadors to the United Nations
title: Sergey Ling
